narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Great if you have a project in mind and want a space to paint. Sam also gives great feedback.
it's great and you'll have a lot of fun if you're confident in yourself as a painter and have ideas to carry you through the semester.
It is a deeper pursuit of your painting passions, with suggestions of projects if you need it. Take it with Messer for sure.
